---
const { image, title, description } = Astro.props;
---

<article class="max-w-screen-lg mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <!-- Top Image -->
  <img
    src="/images/pexels-shkrabaanthony-4599405.webp"
    alt="Relaxing spa experience on the Costa del Sol"
    class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg shadow-md mb-8 object-cover"
  />

  <!-- Title -->
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
    {title}
  </h1>
  <!-- Intro Paragraph -->
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
    The Costa del Sol isn’t just a sun soaked paradise it’s a sanctuary for
    relaxation, wellness, and rejuvenation. Whether you're visiting for a
    romantic escape, a solo retreat, or a pampering weekend, this guide will
    help you unwind in style.
  </p>

  <!-- Sections -->
  <section class="space-y-6 text-gray-700">
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
        1. Start with a <a
          href="/couples-package"
          class="text-blue-600 underline">Couples Massage</a
        > in Estepona
      </h3>
    </div>

    <p>
      Reconnect and relax with a side by side massage tailored to your needs. At <a
        href="/couples-package"
        class="text-blue-600 underline">Massage Art Estepona</a
      >, couples can enjoy a romantic escapes or shared self-care moments
    </p>
  </section>

  <div>
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. Pamper Your Hands and Feet</h3>
    <p>
      Treat yourself to a luxurious <a
        class="text-blue-600 underline"
        href="/manicure-and-pedicure"
        class="text-blue-600 underline"
      >
        manicure and pedicure.</a
      > Choose from classic, shellac, or spa treatments that leave your nails flawless
      and your spirit refreshed. <a
        href="/manicure-and-pedicure"
        class="text-blue-600 underline">Explore nail care options</a
      > in Estepona.
    </p>
  </div>
</article>

<style>
  p {
    font-family: "tenor sans", "tenor sans placeholder", sans-serif;
  }
</style>
